    "Pulse Watch 所有数据均存储在你的设备上，不会上传到任何服务器。健康数据仅从 Apple HealthKit 读取，用于生成本地分析和训练建议。我们不收集任何个人信息。": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse Watch 所有数据均存储在你的设备上，不会上传到任何服务器。健康数据仅从 Apple HealthKit 读取，用于生成本地分析和训练建议。我们不收集任何个人信息。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All Pulse Watch data is stored on your device and never uploaded to any server. Health data is read only from Apple HealthKit for local analysis and training suggestions. We do not collect any personal information."
          }
        }
      }
    },
